quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,46,"Uye zvirokwazvo takatuma Musa nezviratidzo zvedu kuna Farawo nemadzimambo ake (achivakoka kuchitendero chaAllah cheIslaam). Akati: “Zvirokwazvo, ndiri mutumwa waTenzi vepasi rose (vanhu nemaJinn nezvihnu zvese).”"
  43,47,"Asi apo paakasvika kwavari nezviratidzo zvedu kwavari, zvirokwazvo vakazviseka"
  43,48,"Uye hapana chiratidzo chatakavaratidza asi kuti chaiva chikuru kudarika chimwe chacho, uye takavabata nemarwadzo kuti pamwe vangadzoke (kuchitendero chaAllah, Islaam)"
  43,49,"Uye vakati (kuna Musa): “Iwe wemapipi! Tikumbirire kuna Tenzi vako maererano nezvavakakuvimbisa. Zvirokwazvo, tichava tinozvitungamirira (zvakanaka).”"
  43,50,"Asi patakabvisa mutongo kwavari, vakave vanotyora chitsidzo (kuti vaizotenda tikabvisa marwadzo kubva kwavari)"
  43,51,"Uye Farawo akasheedzera kuvanhu vake (achiti): “Imi vanhu vangu! Hausi hwangu here humambo hweEgypt, uye nzizi idzi dzinoyerera pasi pangu? Hamuoni here?”"
  43,52,"“Handisi nani here pane uyu (Musa) wepasi, uye asingagoni kutaura zvinonzwika?”"
  43,53,"“Sei nguwo dzendarama dzisina kuiswa paari, kana kutumwa aine ngirozi?”"
  43,54,"Naizvozvo (Farawo) akafurira vanhu vake uye vakamuteerera. Zvirokwazvo, vange vari vanhu vakapanduka (vasingateereri Allah)"
  43,55,"Naizvozvo pavakatitsamwisa, takavapa murango, uye tikavanyudza vose"
  43,56,Uye takavaita chidzidzo uye muenzaniso kune vaizotevera